Package ui.framework.states

Class AuthenticateSharedState

  • java.lang.Object
    • ui.framework.states.AuthenticateSharedState
  • public class AuthenticateSharedState
extends java.lang.Object
    Maintains shared authentication-related state across the application. This includes the cashier information, manager status, and navigation panel view controller.
